org.eclipse.papyrus.RobotMLLibraries.RobotML_ModelLibrary.RobotML_DataTypes.sensor_datatypes

Interface CarLikeOdometry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CarLikeOdometryImpl

    public interface CarLikeOdometry
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Car Like Odometry'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Header
    • Steering angle
    • Left rear wheel distance
    • Right rear wheel distance
    • Right rear wheel velocity
    • Left rear wheel velocity

    See Also:
    Sensor_datatypesPackage.getCarLikeOdometry()
